papagaio (1.1.0-1ubuntu1) focal; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release
  * Packaging and distribution support
  * PyPI package support
  * Debian package with full structure
  * AUR PKGBUILD for Arch Linux
  * Interactive installer with distro detection
  * Uninstaller script
  * Configuration file support
  * Enhanced papagaio-ctl commands

